You also get Google Feed by swiping right from the homescreen and summon the Google Assistant by long-pressing the home button. Xiaomi Mi A2 is amongst the Best Camera phones at this price point. Also, the powerful Snapdragon 660 processor has so far been restricted to more expensive phones, making this phone a tempting option for someone looking for a performer on a budget.
